---
title: Broccoli Pesto Pasta with Marinated Mozzarella
description: Mix up your weekly meal rotation with something a little different! We've given wholesome broccoli-studded pasta a lift with silky marinated mozzarella, toasty pine nuts and herbaceous pesto!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-au-brocoli-et-au-pesto-1928c078.jpg
